Package: hlapro
Title: Tools to Work with HLA Typings and Single-Antigen Bead Assays
Version: 0.3.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Leon", "Reteig", , "leonreteig@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5814-0992")),
    person("UMC Utrecht", role = c("cph", "fnd"))
  )
Description: Provides tools for Human Leukocyte Antigen (HLA) data:
    genotypes as well as (Luminex) single-antigen bead-based assays.
    Including: standardizing HLA typings to a common format (GL Strings),
    reducing and increasing HLA typing resolution, determining bead
    positivity and assessing donor-specific antibodies (DSAs).
